IC.LIR
Class SethiUllmanWeightVisitor

java.lang.Object
  IC.LIR.SethiUllmanWeightVisitor
All Implemented Interfaces:
IC.AST.Visitor
public class SethiUllmanWeightVisitor
extends java.lang.Object
implements IC.AST.Visitor

Calculate the weight of each AST node (expressions) according to Sethi-Ullman algorithm and determine whether it is optimizable, i.e. contains no expressions that may contain side-effects. The default weight is 0 and the default isOptimise is false.

Author:
arbel
